{
  "stem": "26576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I thought I haven't met one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After the war, I didn't meet anybody from-- from my school days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was-- well, this, because my father was almost an atheist, and-- and my grandmother was desperate-- she wanted me to have the Jewish education.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, not-- she didn't want to tell my father, because she knew she won't succeed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she took me-- she sent me to [POLISH] for quite a few years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was very upset when he learned later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as far as I am concerned, I am very happy now, because I've learned a lot of Judaism, a lot of sort things that I probably would not have learned any other way.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My favorite pastimes-- I am always up to now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm a very good reader.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I read a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember now things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I read much more than a general sort of-- that a girl my age would read, which went with me through life, and it was very useful.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also used to help, occasionally, my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Jews in Poland-- a lot of Jews in Poland would come from little, small villages or larger villages, and their Polish wasn't first class.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So whatever was necessary to use for some kind of-- well, you had to speak good Polish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father would send me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember once a story that my little sister-- I think she was, at that stage, two and a half-- got lost.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somebody said that they saw a policeman taking her to the police station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my-- my father said to me, go and pick up Sala, and-- But don't tell them your name.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
